[[http://www.repmgr.org/][repmgr]], [[http://www.repmgr.org/][replication manager for PostgreSQL clusters]], [[pgsql/pgloader.html][pgloader]], [[pgsql/prefix.html][prefix]],
[[pgsql/preprepare.html][preprepare]], [[pgsql/pgstaging.html][pg_staging]], [[http://villemain.org/projects/pgfincore][pgfincore]] et d'autres encore.

